	   <tr><td colspan=2>hey all,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;      A lot of you monks have been wondering what weapons to equip, and all that stuff.  My suggestion is, DONT EQUIP WEAPONS!  A monk is a damage dealing class, you are required to deal damage to your target before it kills you.  A weapon does alot of damage but most are too slow.  Hand to hand is the best attacking skill for a monk.  Dual weild works with your hands aswell.  So if you have cane of the tranquil or essence of dol or some other weapon either sell it, or twink another character with it.  <br><br>Question: &quot;But my hands dont do a lot of damage!&quot;<br>Answewer: &quot;You need to do little bits of damage quickly not big amouts slowly.<br><br>Question: &quot;I worked hard for my weapon, and i dont want to sell it.&quot;<br>Answer: &quot;I suggest you sell it anyway.  Depending on what it is you could make a lot of money off it, and maybe buy some Wu's or something.&quot;<br><br>Question: &quot;In my higher lvls hand to hand wont be good enough, what do i do then?&quot;<br>Answer: &quot;Keep the hands, as you get better you learn disiplinary skills that do alot of damage, this is the fun part of your monk!&quot;<br><br>Hope this answers some questions for all of you.<br><br>Stronghands<br>Innoruk server<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
