	   <tr><td colspan=2>This monk's opinion?&nbsp;&nbsp;Go Goranga/CoT to level 50, then lose the CoT and go Goranga/Fist.  I think the Wu stick is horribly overpriced and overrated, and in a couple levels you'd want to lose the proc from the Wu any way when aggro starts to become an issue.<br><br>The Goranga is a bit on the slow side compared to the Wu or a Jade Mace, but its ratio is sufficiently higher than the faster weaps to make up for it.  My own back of the envelope figuring says the Goranga is almost as good as a Jade Mace at your level, and some monks have posted that weapons analyzer programs say that the Goranga and the Jade Mace return the same DPS at your level.  JM &gt; Wu, so lose the Wu.<br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
