<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101106316861698></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101106316861698><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=101106316861698>RE: what to use</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=101106316861698#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=35651><span id=Guru>Keyeluke</span></a>, <span id=Guru>Guru</span><br><span id=notbold>589 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Jan 14th 9:52 PM 2002</td>
