	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello, I am a newly dinged 50th level Monk, and also a first char player, so all is new each day.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>My question is about the disciplines we aquire.  I have a 50+ warrior friend that was saying something about allocating a % of exp to skills, and the rest to general exp, is this true for warriors only, or does it apply to all classes?  If true, how do I do it?<br><br>Also, has anyone seen any sites that discuss these new skills?<br><br>Thanks in Advance<br><br>Cramey<br>Lords of the Crimson Cube<br>50th <br>Lanys<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
